$(document).ready(function() {
    var table = $('#example').DataTable({
        searchBuilder: true
    });
    table.searchBuilder.container().prependTo(table.table().container());
});




Foundation



This is the `-init searchbuilder`extension for DataTables. It allows results to be filtered based on a complex search query.

This example shows searchbuilder being used with the [Zurb Foundation](http://foundation.zurb.com/) CSS framework.
